  (E'Gregory', E'Davis', E'Owner', E'Landscape  Investments LLC', NULL, E'greg@fenceinvestments.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Denton, Texas, United States', E'United States', E'Owner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/dallasfence', E'I am pursuing the goal to be the best Fence company in the Dallas Fort Worth area. I provide: Trust - A+ rated from Better Business Bureau Unequaled levels of Superior Service - I, the owner visit every single new project build. I have an English speaking American citizen &amp; Hispanic foreman that our clients love! Experience - I have assembled a team of elite craftsmen with over 48 years in the fence constructing business. Quality products - Full 1X6 pickets, 2X4 premium rails, ring shank nails,.095 Gage galvanized post, plugs, commercial oil based stain... Great Value - I beat the competition in price &amp; service Process - To help guarantee a positive experience for you! Warranty - 5 year warranty I want you to be highly satisfied when we install your new beautiful fencing structure &amp; still satisfied 15 years down the road. The greatest compliment is the referrals I receive from existing clients that open new opportunities with future clients. In the service business, such a testament is the ultimate reward. Customer quote: "Greg, Just wanted to thank you again for building us such a beautiful "fencing structure!" It is everything we hoped for and are extremely pleased with the final product. You were such a pleasure to work with .Your communication, follow up, and solutions to all of our questions and concerns exceeded our expectations. Being in the retail business for over 12 years, I know about customer service. Your level of service exceeded my expectations and quite honestly has surpassed all others that I have experienced since our move to our new home. Thanks again for your hard work and dedication to our project! God Bless, J" Highly satisfying clients since 1986! Specialties: Iron fences, Cedar fence, Spruce fence, Vinyl fence, split rail fence, Board on board or side by side fencing, chain link fences, pipe fence, ranch fence, automated, drive way or fence gates. Concrete or stain concrete, decks, landscape Installations,', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fence-investments-inc', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'Building strong quality fencing, pergolas, patio cover….structures at below market value.', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''gates'', ''arbors'', ''fence company'', ''premium quality'', ''decks'']', E'https://www.fenceinvestments.com', E'1 employee', NULL, E'DFW, Texas, United States', E'Dfw', E'Texas', E'United States', NULL, NULL, E'[''electric'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
  (E'Jim', E'Kodysh', E'General Manager', E'Richtech Industries', NULL, E'jimkodysh@richtechindustries.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Avon Lake, Ohio, United States', E'United States', E'Manager', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jimkodysh', E'"Victory comes from finding opportunities in problems." -Sun Tzu', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/richtech-industries', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'Mission Statement

At Richtech Industries, we are committed to making our customers, our employees, and our company successful. The Richtech business philosophy is:

•Conduct business with uncompromised integrity and professionalism.
•Consistently deliver on our individual and company commitments to our customers.
•Advance innovation in our products.
•Maintain an excellent level of customer service.
•Supply products that meet our professional and personal standards of quality.
•Strive to be our customers'' most valued supplier.


About Richtech Industries

Since 1987, Richtech Industries has been the premier supplier of specialized products for the waterproofing industry.

Our direct-to-contractor business model allows us to focus on delivering the highest quality and service to our customers.

Located outside Cleveland, Ohio, Richtech sells to several hundred waterproofing professionals across the United States.

Richtech sells only to the professional waterproofing contractor. We do not sell to the residential end-user.

Homeowners are encouraged to browse our products and visit the learning center.

Please consult a waterproofing professional in your area for your residential waterproofing needs.', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''diverters'', ''drainage'', ''battery backups'', ''basement waterproofing'', ''pumps'', ''manufacturing-industrial'', ''building-materials'', ''b2b'', ''manufacturing'', ''wholesale'']', E'https://www.richtechindustries.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Avon, Ohio, United States', E'Avon', E'Ohio', E'United States', E'[''800.677.7791'', ''800-677-7791'', ''+1 800 677 7791'']', E'[''orders@richtechindustries.com'', ''sales@richtechindustries.com'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/richtechindustries', E'https://www.twitter.com/richtechind', NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/richtechindustries', E'44738750'),
