ip with the Miami Dade Code officials. This effort led to an MBMA &amp; Miami Dade endorsed code modification to the South Florida HVHZ deflection criteria for structural metal roofing changing it from L/240 to L/180. MBCEA (Metal Building Contractors and Erectors Association): Past Board Member of the Tampa, FL Chapter of the MBCEA Co-author of the MBCEA Retrofit Installation Video Member IIBEC (International Institute of Building Enclosure Consultants) formally, RCI (Roof Consultants Institute) Sertoma Speech and Hearing Foundation: Foundation member since its'' 1980 inception, Board member since 1997.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/roof-hugger-inc-', E'Building Materials', E'Phone: 800-771-1711, email: sales@roofhugger.com 
