ce tables) Restoration (restoring finish, with or without color change) Refinishing (traditional refinishing for badly worn wood surfaces) Please visit our website at www.woodlordrestorations.com or call our office to see what Furniture Medic can do for you!', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/woodlord-restorations', E'Facilities Services', E'Providing excellent service since 1995, Furniture Medic by WoodLord Restorations, located in Pearl River, NY is owned by a 25 year veteran of the New York City Police Department. We serve residential and commercial customers in Rockland & Westchester counties in New York and Bergen & Essex counties New Jersey and surrounding locations. 

