  (E'Tom', E'Koczur', E'President', E'Signature Innovations, LLC', NULL, E'tkoczur@signaturehardwoods.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Elk Grove Village, Illinois, United States', E'United States', E'President/Vice President', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/tom-koczur-3b671710', E'Signature Innovations d.b.a SIGNATURE HARDWOODS™ is Chicagoland’s premier custom designer, manufacturer and installer of true European hand scraped and antiqued hardwood flooring—recognized worldwide for creating beautiful and enduring hardwood floor designs.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/signature-innovations-llc', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'Signature Innovations, LLC d.b.a SIGNATURE HARDWOODS™ is Chicagoland’s premier custom designer, manufacturer and installer of true European bespoke hand-scraped and antiqued hardwood flooring—recognized worldwide for creating beautiful and enduring floor designs. 

SIGNATURE HARDWOODS™ award appointed 4,000 square feet Showroom & Flooring Design Studio is located at 1171 Landmeier Road in Elk Grove Village, Illinois 60007. We are open Monday thru Friday from 8:30 AM until 5:00 PM, and on Saturday by appointment only. We are closed on Sundays.

Established in 2002 with the goal of introducing innovative products using advanced technology, Signature has undoubtedly mastered the art of custom hardwood flooring. Signature is the place for true professionals, designers, architects and builders searching for an exquisite and distinctive design. We cater to those who expect products and service that are unsurpassed by any others in the industry. 

You may ask what sets our company and products apart from other luxury hardwood floor suppliers. Simply put, it is our insistence on using only the finest woods and the most talented European craftsmen, while always maintaining careful awareness for the environment and a dedication to the art and tradition of creating beautiful, enduring floors. It is only at Signature that your feet will find the comfort of such a thoughtfully chosen selection, masterfully worked to last the test of time, for you and your future generations.

