  (E'Jan', E'Tomberg', E'Chief Executive Officer', E'Nordic Steel Gutters', NULL, E'jan@nordicsteelgutters.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Virginia Beach, Virginia, United States', E'United States', E'C-Level', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jan-tomberg-04a36111', E'Managing Director and project leader for business integration. Manager with 20 years of experience within business development, management and international sales. Experienced in developing long-term customer relations and business development. Strong in employee coaching and project management.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nordic-steel-gutters', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'At Nordic Steel Gutters, we bring the precision, durability, and timeless design of Scandinavian engineering to the American market. Our half-round steel gutter systems are crafted with 23-gauge galvanized steel and coated with GreenCoat® technology, making them one of the most durable and environmentally responsible options available today.
 
