  (E'Dan', E'Barger', E'Managing Member', E'Apollo Plumbing and Drain Cleaning', NULL, E'dan@apolloplumbing.net', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Everett, Washington, United States', E'United States', E'Manager', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/dan-barger-08613720', E'General Manager at Apollo Plumbing since 2005. Specialties: Plumbing service: water heaters, trench-less water service lines, repairs, remodels, new installations, and general service. Areas Served: Seattle, Bothell, Everett, Marysville, Mukilteo, Lake Stevens, Snohomish and north King Counties.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/apollo-plumbing-llc', E'Consumer Services', E'Back in 2005, Dan Barger decided there had to be a better way to provide plumbing here where he grew up. He had worked with big corporate plumbing companies and felt there was something missing—a personal touch.

