  (E'Kenneth', E'Jagr', E'Commercial Sales & Account Manager', E'Air Professional Associates LLC', NULL, E'ken@airprofs.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'North Salem, New York, United States', E'United States', E'Manager', E'Sales', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/kenneth-jagr', E'Demonstrated success in securing multimillion-dollar sales, while providing award-winning sales leadership in highly volatile markets. Adept at driving the growth of company revenues and improving sales-team performance. Tenacious in building a new business, securing customer loyalty, and forging strong relationships with external business partners. Multiple recent successes in the energy efficiency and conservation industry implementing several Con Edison incentive programs. Proficient in lead generation, auditing, selling, and implementation of energy efficiency measures with a proven record of accomplishment.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/airprofs', E'Consumer Services', E'Over the years, we have provided heating, ventilating and air conditioning systems for residential and commercial premises of all sizes. 

We have serviced homes ranging in size from 1,000 sq. ft. to 45,000 sq. ft.

On the commercial side, we are known for our unique design-build capability from conception to final installation and start-up. We recently completed or are still involved in the following design-build projects:

*Private school gymnasium and support facilities such as locker rooms, etc.

*20,000 sq. ft. offices for corporate headquarters with attached warehouse.

*Community Center with indoor swimming pool complex, gymnasium, locker facilities and related exercise and training spaces.

*Office for private aircraft support facilities at West Chester County Airport.

*45,000 sq. ft. medical device manufacturing facility, with various temperature and humidity requirements for the separate areas of the building.

In addition to design and installation, you can also count on Air Professionals to provide preventative maintenance, timely service and repairs by our highly trained staff, including 24/7 after-hours and emergency service.

At Air Professional Associates, we nurture and maintain an atmosphere of excellence among all team members. Each of our installers and technicians is trained on a regular, ongoing basis. We, and they, are certified by the following industry organizations:

*North American Technicina Excellence (NATE)

*Air Conditioning Contractor''s Association (ACCA)

*U.S. Better Business Bureau (BBB)

