  (E'Steven', E'West', E'Senior Project Manager', E'Metcalf Painting & Flooring', NULL, E'swest@metcalfpainting.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Cary, North Carolina, United States', E'United States', E'Senior', E'Project Management', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/steven-west-765a0110', E'OVERWHELMED BY A REPAINT PROJECT? ❓ Not sure where to start, how to manage the details, or who to trust to get it done right? I help homeowners and business managers eliminate the stress of repaint projects by creating clear plans, ensuring quality at every step, and delivering results that transform spaces. PAST – MY JOURNEY TO HOME IMPROVEMENT My career began in a completely different world—scientific research. While managing a lab, I discovered my natural talent for organization and problem-solving. On weekends, I built a landscaping business, where I thrived on meeting clients, improving homes, and delivering results that transformed spaces. This hands-on work made me realize my passion for helping people create better environments, paving the way for a career in home improvement and painting. PRESENT – WHAT DRIVES ME Today, I specialize in helping homeowners and business managers achieve stress-free, high-quality repaint projects. My role as a painting professional allows me to: • 🎯 Develop efficient project plans that save time and reduce headaches. • 🎨 Transform spaces into inspiring environments that reflect my clients'' goals. • 🤝 Lead teams with empathy and clear communication to deliver exceptional results. • 🛠 Solve complex problems on-site with innovative solutions and a customer-first mindset. Every project I take on is an opportunity to combine my organizational expertise with my passion for delivering results that make a lasting impact. FUTURE – WHAT’S NEXT My vision is to refine business systems that simplify painting projects for both clients and teams. I aim to: • 📈 Build a scalable model that ensures consistent quality and care for all projects. • 💡 Create a culture of growth, pride, and innovation within my team. • 🌟 Raise the industry standard by delivering predictable, top-tier results every time. LET’S CONNECT! If you''re a homeowner or business manager looking for someone who can transform your repaint project into a seamless experience, let’s talk! Whether you need practical advice or expert execution, I’m here to help. 📩 Message me here on LinkedIn or reach out to start the conversation.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/metcalf-painting-%26-interiors', E'Construction', E'Metcalf Painting & Flooring has specialized in exterior/interior residential and commercial painting as well as many other related services since 1986. At Metcalf Painting and Flooring, we pride our company on top quality, loyal and distinct service, bringing extensive knowledge and attention to each and every project.', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''commercial painting'', ''commercial flooring'', ''residential painting'', ''residential flooring'', ''painting'', ''flooring'', ''customer service'', ''commercial'', ''residential'']', E'https://www.metcalfpainting.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Cary, North Carolina, United States', E'Cary', E'North Carolina', E'United States', E'[''1-919-469-4877'', ''469-1817'', ''(919) 469-1817'']', E'[''info@metcalfpainting.com'']', E'[''amp'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/pages/metcalf-painting-interiors/617107034995442', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'28172026'),
