  (E'Mason', E'Nichols', E'Vice President of Operations', E'Tri-Tex Roof Systems', NULL, E'mason@tritexroofing.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Austin, Texas, United States', E'United States', E'President/Vice President', E'Operations', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/mason-nichols-a37395153', E'As the Vice President of Operations at Tri-Tex Roof Systems, I proudly bring a diverse background and a steadfast commitment to excellence to every project I oversee. My professional journey began in the food service industry, where I honed my skills in customer service, operational efficiency, and team management. Five years ago, I made the strategic transition to the roofing industry, joining the incredible team at Tri-Tex Roof Systems. Since then, my growth both personally and professionally has been profound. I have the privilege of working closely with our dedicated crews, engaging with customers, and ensuring homeowner satisfaction at every step of our projects. My role has expanded to encompass many responsibilities typically associated with project management, allowing me to integrate operational oversight with hands-on project execution. I am deeply invested in the success of Tri-Tex Roof Systems and am proud of the integral role I play in driving our company''s growth and ensuring the highest standards of service. My passion for building strong client relationships and fostering a collaborative team environment continues to fuel my commitment to our collective success. Outside of work, I enjoy immersing myself in the great outdoors. Whether I''m fishing in the serene lakes and rivers of Texas or searching for arrowheads that tell tales of history, these hobbies provide me with relaxation and a sense of connection to nature and the past.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tri-tex-roof-systems', E'Construction', E'Tri-Tex Roof Systems is a trusted Central Texas roofing and storm restoration company serving residential, commercial, and new construction clients since 2008.

Backed by deep expertise in roofing, insurance, mortgage, and real estate, we bring insight and care to every project—from first inspection to final walk-through.

We specialize in:
🔹 Commercial roofing: proactive inspections, capital planning, system replacements
🔹 Residential storm restoration: documentation, insurance guidance, peace of mind
🔹 New construction roofing: reliable installs, builder coordination, long-term performance

Our commercial division supports property managers, facility directors, ownership groups, and builders with transparent timelines, seasoned crews, and long-term roof protection strategies.

What sets us apart: 
✔️ We help you understand your roof’s risk before the storm
✔️ We guide you through the claims process with speed and clarity
✔️ We deliver dependable results—with zero pressure, always

Tri-Tex is proud to partner with realtors, adjusters, builders, and commercial decision-makers across Central Texas.

Let’s protect what matters—one roof at a time.', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''roofing services'', ''storm restoration'', ''emergency roof repairs'', ''insurance claims assistance'', ''hail damage repair'', ''wind damage restoration'', ''roof inspections'', ''commercial roofing'', ''residential roofing'', ''roof maintenance solutions'', ''public adjustor coordination'', ''roof inspection reports for insurance claims'', ''supplemental claim handling'', ''detailed estimates for insurance purposes'', ''insurance claim advocacy'', ''hail & storm damage assessment'', ''insurance claims coordination'', ''roof replacement & installation'', ''commercial'', ''residential'', ''solutions'', ''roofing'', ''customized'']', E'https://www.tritexroofing.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Austin, Texas, United States', E'Austin', E'Texas', E'United States', E'[''(512) 583-0500'']', E'[''help@tritexroofing.com'']', E'[''amp'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/tritexroofsystems/about', NULL, NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/tritexroofs', NULL),
