  (E'Jamie', E'Addison', E'Customer Service Manager', E'Cement Tile Shop', NULL, E'jamie@cementtileshop.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Greater Tampa Bay Area United States', E'United States', E'Manager', E'Customer Service', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jamie-addison-mba-83324030', E'I graduated from the International Academy of Merchandising and Design in Tampa, Florida with a B.A. in Merchandising Management and minor in Interior Design during which I also owned and operated my own clothing store. I relocated to San Francisco where I continued with a retail management career. I transferred with the company to the San Diego location, to help maximize sales and improve customer service, as well as the overall look of the store. I moved back home to Tampa, Florida in preparation for a move to England to continue my education at the American Intercontinental University with the MBA program. I have completed the MBA program and moved back to Tampa where I became General Manager for PAPYRUS. After taking time off for some home renovations, I am now Customer Service Manager for Cement Tile Shop.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cement-tile-shop', E'Retail', E'As America''s leading supplier of handmade cement tile, we offer in-stock patterns and solid colors as well as special order material. We have warehouses in Arizona, Florida and Europe and typically ship in-stock tile within 48 hours.

