  (E'Jeffrey', E'Niegsch', E'Owner / Operator', E'Complete Aquatic Solutions', NULL, E'jeffrey@casarizona.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Queen Creek, Arizona, United States', E'United States', E'Owner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jeffrey-l-niegsch-14a9b119', E'I’ve spent over 20 years in the swimming pool industry, working in the Arizona sun, handling everything from complex repairs to business operations. I’ve built strong relationships with customers and earned a reputation for solving problems others walk away from. But after years of physical labor, minor health issue, and my age, I had to face a hard truth: I couldn’t keep working the way I always had. That challenge led to opportunity. I began building tools to make my business run without me in the field — and ended up creating a full AI-powered assistant named “Billy.” Billy reads and categorizes emails, automates billing through QuickBooks, remembers customer history, and flags important messages — all with zero code. I built him using real-world problems I faced every day as a pool pro. Since then, I’ve developed: A DIY chatbot that helps homeowners troubleshoot and repair pool issues A smart memory system that simulates long-term context for business tasks Automations that save hours each week on billing, communication, and scheduling I didn’t come from tech — I came from trenches, from pulling engines, and transmissions, to installing filters, and pumps, repairing leaks, and long summers. Now I’m turning the knowledge I earned the hard way into tools other pool professionals and service-based businesses can use to work smarter, stay organized, and protect their health and time.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/complete-aquatic-solutions', E'Consumer Services', E'We are dedicated to providing a wide variety of superior pool products and maintenance services for both commercial and residential properties. We believe in building and maintaining outstanding relationships, and we are dedicated to giving you the education, professionalism, and quality of work you, business, and family deserve. We take pride in the work done on each and every time and guarantee your satisfaction. We look forward to the opportunity to work with you, and look forward to providing your Complete Aquatic Solutions.', E'[''pool services'', ''residential swimming pool'', ''spa'', ''water feature maintenance'', ''commercial swimming pool'', ''& water feature maintenance'', ''acid wash'', ''tile cleaning'', ''green pool specialists'', ''plaster repair'', ''filter cleaning'', ''pool drain & refill'', ''pool repair'', ''water analysis'', ''pool maintenance'', ''pool service'', ''pool filter cleaning'']', E'https://www.completeaquaticsolutions.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Chandler, Arizona, United States', E'Chandler', E'Arizona', E'United States', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/completeaquaticsolutions', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'21883462'),
