  (E'Rachel', E'King', E'Office Manager', E'DependaCoat/DependaRoof/DependaGutters', NULL, E'rachel@dependacoat.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Greater Augusta Area United States', E'United States', E'Manager', E'Administrative', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/rachel-king-b9359b190', E'Office Manager, Marketing Specialist and Accounts Executive for a locally owned and family owned and operated business in the CSRA, DependaCoat/DependaRoof/DependaGutters.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dependacoat-dependaroof-dependagutters', E'Specialty Trade Contractors', E'We are a locally owned as well as family owned an operated business in the CSRA specializing in exterior and interior painting, residential and commercial roofing and gutters and gutter guards. 

DependaCoat: Never Paint Again! We Don’t Just Cover It, Our Carpenters Restore It!
DependaCoat''s Lifetime Architectural Coating is a high-quality exterior coating system that offers superior durability and protection for your home or building. Developed and tested as an alternative superior to paint, stain, and vinyl siding. DependaCoat LAC outlasts and outperforms conventional paints and coatings on residential, commercial, and industrial buildings. With its combination of durability, affordability, and aesthetic appeal, DependaCoat provides unparalleled long-term value, providing a permanent exterior paint alternative.

DependaRoof: Lifetime Shingles – Metal Roofs – Preferred Provider for ALL Insurance Companies!
From the smallest leak repair to a complete roof replacement, we deliver the same professionalism, dedication, and customer satisfaction. Whether you have a residential house with a standard composition shingle roof, a commercial building with a built-up asphalt and gravel roof or a large building with a compound roof coating, new construction or minor or major roof repairs, DependaRoof should be your first choice.

DependaGutters: Premium Custom Seamless Gutters – Stainless Steel DependaGutters Platinum Guards!
At DependaGutters our skilled installers use only premium gutters, downspouts, and gutter guards from the top manufacturers, and we pride ourselves in helping our customers make the best choices they can. We offer the industry''s best solution for keeping your gutters clean and free of debris. Our DependaGutters Platinum Guards will completely revolutionize the way you take care of your roof.', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''residential and commercial'', ''gutter guards'', ''gutters'', ''roofing'', ''paint coating'', ''painting'', ''exterior painting'', ''rain gutters'', ''home repair'', ''home maintenance'', ''contractor'', ''architectural coatings'', ''deck staining'']', E'https://www.dependacoat.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Augusta, GA, United States', E'Augusta', E'Georgia', E'United States', E'[''706-550-1485'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/dependacoat', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
