Why choose MVM?
MVM is a locally owned, family operated company who specialize in masonry restoration/new construction commercial and residential servicing the greater Mississippi Valley area. We offer a menu of services from helping our customers select materials consistent with their style whether its Vintage, Conventional or New Age, keeping things cost effective and within budget- to pattern design, color coordination/distribution and installation. We stay competitive through creative thinking, an artistic approach and attention to detail bringing your idea to life. 

What can you expect from MVM?
When you team up with MVM you team up with the best in the business. Through trial and error and over twenty years of combined trade experience we tackle some of the most challenging projects some contractors shy away from. You can trust that your experience will be simple and hassle free. Ingrained in MVM are three basic principles we follow to ensure quality and a great customer experience. Our mission is to provide the highest level of professionalism, integrity and effectiveness in the industry. Reputation does matter and we value your business just as much as you appreciate the work we do. That’s why we do everything we can to protect that by branding ourselves with these basic principles.', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''masonry'', ''stone work'', ''plastering'', ''fireplaces'', ''stucco services'', ''residential'', ''concrete'', ''masonry specialists'', ''commercial'']', E'https://www.mississippivalleymasonry.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'La Crosse, WI, United States', E'La Crosse', E'Wisconsin', E'United States', E'[''608-881-6400'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/mvmlax', NULL, E'https://www.youtube.com/@bryanmolzahn1086', NULL, NULL),
