  (E'Arthur', E'Slade', E'Plumber', E'One Call Services | Plumbing * Heating * Cooling', NULL, E'arthur@azplumbers.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Mesa, Arizona, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Trades', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/arthur-slade-a9a378242', NULL, E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/one-call-services-plumbing-heating-cooling', E'Consumer Services', E'"One Call" provides Plumbing Repair, Air Conditioning and Heating Repair services in Phoenix Arizona.

The solution for your residential & Commercial plumbing repair problems!
We inspect your home for needed plumbing repairs, then provide a free estimate!

One Call Services provides residential plumbing repair, home A/C installation and repair, and heating installation and repair in Mesa, Tempe, Scottsdale and the east valley.	

The plumbing technicians at One Call Plumbing Services are trained experts in all types of plumbing services and maintenance, including faucet leaks, clogged drains, water leaks in piping and fixtures, sewer line issues, toilet back-ups, garbage disposals, and water heaters. You can be confidant that our licensed plumbers will perform all plumbing repair tasks perfectly and at an affordable price.

One Call Plumbing Services will provide you with a value-packed, honest, professional, quality residential plumbing services and products. Our staff will always respect you and your home. Our clean, courteous, professionally dressed plumbers and service technicians will care for your home better than any other plumbing services company - we promise!!

