  (E'Malki', E'David', E'owner', E'Mike''s Locksmith, LLC', NULL, E'mike@mikes-locksmith.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Rockville, Maryland, United States', E'United States', E'Owner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/malkidavid', E'We provide commercial, institutional and residential locksmith and security services in Washington, DC and Maryland. We strive to give our clients excellent customer service and honest advise concerning all of their security needs. All our estimates are free of charge; all materials and labor are guaranteed. All of our pricing is upfront, so there are never any surprises. For our valued clients, we offer Emergency Lockout Services. Our company, Mike''s Locksmith &amp; Security is a certified dealer of Mul-T-Lock, the best, most secure lock on the market. Other services we provide are: high-security locks, keyless entry deadbolts, standard door hardware, home automation, access control, alarm systems, security cameras, time and attendance systems and time clocks, synchronized wall clocks and bells. Mike''s Locksmith &amp; Security can help you with all of your security needs. Visit my Company Page and follow me, http://www.linkedin.com/company/2917995 Contact me at 240-506-7500 or at mike@mikes-locksmith.com for a free consultation of your security needs. Visit our store at: 1100 Taft Stre., Rockville, MD 20850', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mike%27s-locksmith', E'Retail', E'Mike''s Locksmith & Security is an award winning, highly regarded locksmith and security business serving Washington, DC and Suburban Maryland. Mike''s offers state-of-the-art high security solutions for business and residences, as well as institutions. 
We provide the following products and services: high-security locks, keyless entry deadbolts, standard door hardware, rekeying, home automation, access control, alarm systems, security cameras, time and attendance systems and time clocks, synchronized wall clocks and bells.

We are available to our valued customers for emergencies or by appointment at your convenience.
