  (E'Robyn', E'Ingersole', E'Sales and Marketing', E'Jenbrook Australia', NULL, E'robyn.i@napproducts.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Stevenson Ranch, California, United States', E'United States', E'C-Level', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/robyn-ingersole-a3582520', E'NAP is not just a business - it''s my passion. With decades in the natural ingredients industry and having my own essential oil range, I started Naturally Australian Products (NAP) as a U.S. ingredient supply company in 2012 with my business and life partner, Bryan. We acquired 1,147 acres of tea tree in the late 80''s, and another 1,000 acres in 2012. We started with our very own streamlined supply of wild-harvested and plantation-grown tea tree oil to bring a better quality oil to the U.S. Now, nearing 10 years on, NAP has expanded and supplies the U.S with premium ingredients from 30+ countries around the world. We continue to wild-craft on our 2000+ acres Tea Tree farm, which we have converted to Certified Organic land.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jenbrook-australia', E'Wholesale', E'Since 1989 Jenbrook Australia has grown, distilled and supplied certified organic tea tree products to international markets including USA, Korea, Japan, Germany, France and Switzerland.

