  (E'Michael', E'Cohen', E'Founder', E'Tribeca Stone', NULL, E'michael@tribecastone.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'New York, New York, United States', E'United States', E'Founder', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/michael-cohen-79258a53', E'A 20 year stone and tile industry veteran, Michael Cohen’s latest venture, Tribeca Stone was launched to bring the world’s finest product to the world’s most discerning architects, designers, and developers. Tribeca Stone clients expect – and receive – keen attention to detail as well as discriminating taste. Michael personally visits quarries and factories around the world to ensure that his clients receive the best materials available. His dedication to discovering, manufacturing and offering unique stone and tile to his clients is unparalleled. Michael was a founding partner at Allstone Corporation, a global stone and tile distributor and established its flagship showroom at the Boston Design Center. When he is not traveling on behalf of Tribeca Stone clients, Michael lives in Tribeca with his wife and sons, Jackson and Mayer.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tribeca-stone', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'At Tribeca Stone, we are passionate about sourcing the best stone and most innovative tile from around the world. We deliver the finest products and original designs to our clients at the most competitive price possible. 

We are leaders in commercial and residential stone furnishing, devoted to our projects and relentlessly focused on bringing the latest in classical and modern design to New York and North America.

SERVICE
Like the neighborhood where we live and work, Tribeca Stone has a boutique attitude and a global reach. 

Our business is based on direct referrals from our satisfied clientele. Our process is simple, we meet with our clients, listen first, and only then provide, thoughtful, expert advice that continues to make us the first choice of award-winning architects and design professionals. 

We operate around the world, on any scale, and have delivered meticulous service to the largest and most demanding national chains. Our volume and worldwide network of vendors permits us to go straight to the source – cutting through multiple levels of middlemen and distributors to deliver rare, high quality product at an exceptional cost. 

We are on time, every time. 

Tribeca Stone makes your project work.', E'[''retail flooring'', ''hospitality tile and stone'', ''commercial tile and stone'', ''custom mosaic'', ''building material'', ''manufacturing'', ''wholesale'']', E'https://www.instagram.com/tribecastone', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Manhattan, New York, United States', E'Manhattan', E'New York', E'United States', E'[''212.518.3669'', ''+1 212 518 3669'']', E'[''info@tribecastone.com'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/tribecastonenyc', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'24169318'),
