gallery.com/ 📍 126 S Broadway, De Pere, WI 54115', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tile-stone-gallery-wisconsin', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'Tile & Stone Gallery is the area’s only flooring design center that specializes in hard surfaces. Whether you’re looking for high-end “wow” or everyday durability, our team will source the right flooring option to suit your needs and budget. Stop by our beautiful, vibrant showroom to get a taste for what we offer!', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''flooring'', ''builders'', ''hard surfaces'', ''homeowners'', ''designers'', ''advice'', ''building material'', ''retail'']', E'https://www.tile-stonegallery.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'De Pere, Wisconsin, United States', E'De Pere', E'Wisconsin', E'United States', E'[''920.632.7304'', ''1-920-632-4792'', ''+1 920 632 4792'', ''920.632.4792'']', E'[''info@tile-stonegallery.com'']', E'[''amp'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/thetileandstonegallery', NULL, NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/tilestonegallery', E'33748142'),
