  (E'Whitney', E'Belkowitz', E'President and CEO', E'Intelligent Concrete LLC', NULL, E'whitney@intelligent-concrete.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Elbert, Colorado, United States', E'United States', E'C-Level', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/whitney-belkowitz-920a00154', NULL, E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/intelligent-concrete', E'Research', E'AT INTELLIGENT CONCRETE WE SPECIALIZE IN MAKING CONCRETE DO THE IMPOSSIBLE. THROUGH THE USE OF EMERGING TECHNOLOGIES AND STATE-OF-THE-ART TESTING OUR GOAL IS TO PRODUCE A SUPERIOR CONCRETE TAILORED TO YOUR UNIQUE NEEDS.', E'[''construction'', ''concrete'', ''science & research'', ''consulting'', ''engineering'', ''concretetesting'', ''design'', ''testing'', ''development'', ''manufacturing-industrial'', ''building-materials'', ''3d printing'', ''product design'', ''publishing'']', E'https://www.intelligent-concrete.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Colorado Springs, Colorado, United States', E'Colorado Springs', E'Colorado', E'United States', E'[''+1 720 636 3657'', ''(720) 636-3657'']', E'[''info@intelligent-concrete.com'', ''admin@intelligent-concrete.com'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/intelligentconcrete', E'https://www.twitter.com/int_concrete', E'https://www.youtube.com/@intelligentconcrete', E'https://www.instagram.com/intelligentconcrete_wb', NULL),
  (E'Brent', E'Links', E'CEO and Founder', E'Advanced Component Services', NULL, E'blinks@acsend2end.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Snoqualmie, Washington, United States', E'United States', E'Founder', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/brent-links-b9850a3a', E'Advanced Component Service (ACS) Founded in 2006 to provide global design, engineering, and sourcing solutions for industrial companies, primarily in the commercial foodservice sector, ACS has evolved to meet the demands of the modern marketplace. We now offer a powerful combination of traditional strengths and cutting-edge marketing services. Our services include: Core Services: Global Product Development &amp; Sourcing (China, England, United States): ACS leverages its global network and decades of experience to provide comprehensive product development and sourcing solutions. We specialize in identifying cost-saving opportunities and optimizing supply chains. Services include design/engineering, material selection, process optimization, and quality control. Cost Reduction Consulting: ACS utilizes a proven consulting methodology to analyze operations and identify cost reduction opportunities. Our approach involves assessment, component analysis, and strategic sourcing. We provide recommendations and support to achieve cost savings. E-commerce Marketing Division: Amazon Optimization: A+ Content, product listing optimization, and SEO strategies to maximize visibility and conversions. We create engaging A+ Content and optimize listings with keywords and SEO to improve search rankings. Visual Content: Photo enhancement and video production to showcase products effectively. We provide photo editing/enhancement and produce videos to highlight product features, benefits, and applications, driving customer engagement. Digital Marketing: Strategic marketing planning and implementation to drive online growth. ACS develops and implements digital marketing strategies, including social media, email, paid advertising, and performance tracking, to increase brand awareness and achieve online growth objectives. ACS leverages 50+ years of combined leadership experience and its global network to provide comprehensive solutions that drive growth and profitability for our clients. We are committed to delivering exceptional results and building long-term partnerships, providing valuable solutions for businesses in today''s competitive marketplace.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/advanced-component-services', E'Wholesale', E'Started in 2006, Advanced Component Services (ACS) is a contract manufacturer, commercial component distributor, e-commerce third party seller and, since 2014, an Amazon Vendor. ACS operates its main office and distribution center in the Seattle area and has support offices and warehouses in China and England.

Commercial Division

From its inception, ACS has operated as a contract manufacturer and commercial distributor primarily focused on developing and selling components used in commercial food service equipment, beverage equipment and lighting.

ACS has manufactured over 4,000 different products for its commercial customers. We directly or indirectly supply components to companies operating supermarkets, c-stores, bakeries, coffee shops, restaurants, office coffee service businesses and other types of establishments.

In addition to the products manufactured by our company, we maintain a large inventory of popular components from companies such as Robertshaw, Parker, Southco, Oetiker and several other fully stocked lines.

ACS is constantly looking for new products to manufacture for our existing and new commercial customers.

E-Commerce Division

In 2014, ACS launched an e-commerce division as part of a strategic initiative to create new revenue streams for its products. The e-commerce division has been very successful and has generated triple-digit growth since its creation. At the end of its fourth year, the e-commerce division was actively marketing and selling tens of thousands of products through a flow of up to 20,000 orders each month.

To support its e-commerce division’s growth, ACS is actively seeking new partnerships with component manufacturers and authorized distribution companies to purchase as many new products as possible to add to its product offering.

