  (E'Tom', E'Hume', E'Director Strategic Partnerships', E'StaticWorx, Inc', NULL, E'tom@staticworx.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Atlanta, Georgia, United States', E'United States', E'Director', E'Sales', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/tom-hume-961791a', E'Static-control flooring is a tiny island in the giant sea of commercial flooring. Yet it’s the least understood, most technically challenging part of the flooring world. My job is to bring clarity to every project, by sharing objective, evidence-based information, helping partners wade through the complexities of testing, floor prep, ESD specs and compliance, and helping them avoid costly mistakes that can affect their wallet or their reputation. 

At StaticWorx, I collaborate closely with architects, designers, and contractors, translating complex technical details into real-world solutions that satisfy mutual objectives. If you’re looking for a partner who listens, genuinely cares, and will always do right by you, let’s connect. 

StaticWorx is responsible for sharing most of the publicly available static-control flooring learning content, the below article is a subject the design community has found most interesting.

https://staticworx.com/learning_center/esd-flooring-technical-information/conductive-versus-dissipative/', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/staticworx', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'StaticWorx provides high-performance static-control flooring systems engineered for mission-critical environments. Our GroundSafe® ESD flooring platforms prevent random electrostatic discharge (ESD) events in electronics manufacturing, SMT facilities, cleanrooms, labs, data centers, and any operation working with sensitive or high-speed electronic components.

Every solution begins with an assessment of your environment, risks, and performance thresholds. From there, we design a complete system that includes the optimal flooring material along with the correct installation method, grounding strategy, footwear protocols, seating, mobile carts, and other elements that influence charge generation and dissipation.

Our portfolio supports a wide range of technical and operational requirements:
– ShadowFX® SDT carpet tile
– AmeriWorx™ conductive and static-dissipative vinyl tile
– Eclipse™ EC and Eclipse Plus™ conductive rubber
– GroundWorx™ ESD epoxy and coatings
– GroundLock™ Extreme interlocking tile

Our agile team of ESD-control specialists supports architects, designers, engineers, contractors, and facilities managers with deep technical knowledge and real-world insight. We collaborate closely with teams in electronics manufacturing, aerospace, cleanrooms, government, healthcare, and advanced technology to ensure alignment with ANSI/ESD S20.20 and operational requirements.

All StaticWorx GroundSafe® floors are backed by a lifetime warranty for static control. After installation, we continue to support clients through testing, verification, and system optimization.

With StaticWorx, you gain a partner committed to the long-term performance of your ESD flooring system and the reliability of your operations.', E'[''esd flooring systems'', ''eclipse ec rubber and eclipse plus'', ''groundlock interlocking tile'', ''ameriworx conductive and dissipative vinyl'', ''groundworx ultra and basics esd epoxy'', ''aia/idec ceu workshops'', ''construction'', ''construction/building materials'', ''esd flooring'', ''carpet tile'', ''chairs'', ''rubber tile'', ''bolt seating'']', E'https://www.staticworx.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Williston, Vermont, United States', E'Williston', E'Vermont', E'United States', E'[''617-923-2000'', ''+1 617-923-2000'']', E'[''info@staticworx.com'']', E'[''microsoft'', ''twitter'', ''google tag manager'', ''youtube'', ''linkedin'', ''instagram'', ''well'', ''mailchimp'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/staticworx', E'https://www.twitter.com/staticworx', NULL, NULL, E'13638160'),
  (E'Beatriz', E'Mendoza', E'Vice President', E'Acquality Pool Service Corp', NULL, E'beatriz@acqualitypool.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Miami, Florida, United States', E'United States', E'President/Vice President', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/butis73', E'I am a creative writer with a passion for storytelling. As an experienced media professional turned business owner I apply what I learned in the past 20 years of writing, producing, and promoting content to my own pool services company. I am in charge of planning and executing the online marketing efforts of the company.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/acqualitypool', E'Consumer Services', E'With 15+ years of pool maintenance experience, the experts at Acquality Pool provide quality pool cleaning service that is punctual, discreet, reliable and professional. We are a family owned and operated business run by a husband and wife team.

