  (E'Pedro', E'Ferrer', E'Founder', E'TechRx Phone & Tablet Repair', NULL, E'pferrer@yourphonefixed.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Greater Macon United States', E'United States', E'Owner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/pedro-ferrer-723a964', E'With 20+ years in the customer service industry Pedro “Pete” Ferrer founded TechRx smartphone and tablet repair in 2013 driven by the combination of a passion for mobile electronics, a passion for repair and an instinct for entrepreneurship. Pete is mostly excited about witnessing and being part of the birth of the mobile device repair industry which in a short time has reached over 4 Billion dollars a year in revenue. TechRx with retail units in Warner Robins, Macon and Dublin, Ga offers a wide variety of accessory and repair solutions for devices including, but not limited to Apple iPhone, iPads, Samsung, Motorola, LG, Nexus, ZTE, Android, and anything else we can get our hands on. *Update- In August of 2017 we decided to join CPR Cell Phone Repair the nations largest phone repair franchise. We did this to facilitate access to national accounts that will allow us to better serve our customers with better pricing, nationwide lifetime warranty, training, OEM parts, in house warranty and insurance claims among several other benefits. You will see a transition of brand name change, but the same ownership, employees, quality repairs and service will be guaranteed.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/techrx-phone-%26-tablet-repair', E'Retail', E'TechRx is a fast and reliable repair solution for the mobile devices that we heavily depend on for our day to day use. We keep thousands of OEM quality parts in stock so your phone or tablet can be repaired and back to work same day, usually while you wait. We continuously train on new products and travel to the best industry training courses along with invest in the best equipment to insure we stay #1 in the industry, allowing us to confidently offer the best warranties on repairs in the industry. TechRx proudly plays a part in conservation by promoting repair vs replace and by recycling the broken parts that would otherwise end up in our landfills contributing to the millions of non-degradeable eWaste and also offering a Buy Back program that puts money back in your pocket for old devices that can be refurbished and sold to customers needing a less expensive solution. TechRx is also an authorized reseller for premium accessories like OtterBox, LifeProof, PureGear, Ballistic and premium Tempered Glass screen protectors with life time warranties. TechRx is a young company that is quickly growing with currently 3 locations in Middle Ga and 2 additional locations in the works to open early 2017.', E'[''electronics repair'', ''iphone screen repair'', ''ipad screen repair'', ''samsung galaxy screen repair'', ''batteries'', ''power button'', ''speaker'', ''microphone'', ''lcd'', ''water damage'', ''motorola'', ''lg'', ''buy and sell used phones'', ''accessories'', ''tempered glass screen protection'', ''ipad repair'', ''android repair'', ''phone repair'', ''tablet repair'', ''iphone repair'']', E'https://www.yourphonefixed.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Warner Robins, Georgia, United States', E'Warner Robins', E'Georgia', E'United States', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
