  (E'Dawn', E'V', E'Comfort Specialist--Sales', E'GV''s Heating & Cooling', NULL, E'dvickers@gvshvac.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Glenview, Illinois, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Customer Service', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/dawnvickers', E'Hi there! I''m Dawn, General Manager at a leading HVAC company at GVs Heating and Cooling. Don''t be surprised if you were expecting Don - I''m the woman behind the free estimate. Working in a male-dominated industry has its challenges, but it''s all worth it when we can provide our clients with the best service possible. At GVs, we don''t just sell boxes - we focus on finding the true value for our clients. That''s why we joined the National Comfort Institute in 2010 and started implementing static pressure and temperature testing on every sales call. #HVAC #ComfortSpecialist #NationalComfortInstitute 💨❄️ As she embarks on the next chapter of her professional journey, Dawn is excited to confront new obstacles and seize the opportunities that lie ahead. Guided by faith and a passion for the industry, she is eager to leverage her extensive experience and knowledge to further enhance the services offered by the family business. With a focus on innovation and customer satisfaction, Dawn looks forward to making a meaningful impact in the HVAC sector for years to come. Dawn is a dedicated and passionate individual, both in her professional life and personal endeavors. With a strong commitment to community engagement, she spends her free time immersed in the world of hockey, where she delights in watching her son play and showcasing his talent on the ice. This enthusiasm for the sport extends beyond mere observation; she actively contributes by coaching the "Learn to Skate" program, where she inspires young children who are eager to learn the fundamentals of skating. Her nurturing approach helps instill confidence and joy in these new skaters as they embark on their journey in the sport. In addition to her commitments in athletics, Dawn holds her faith as the cornerstone of her life. She believes deeply in the teachings of her faith and strives to embody the principles found within, particularly the directive to "Love the Lord your God with all your heart, with all your soul and with all your mind." This unwavering devotion shapes her outlook on both her personal and professional relationships, guiding her interactions with kindness, integrity, and respect. Transforming the HVAC Experience | Leading the Way Since 2006 | Dedicated to Customer Satisfaction | Discover the GVs Difference Today! #HVACExperience #CustomerSatisfaction #GVsDifference 👩‍🔧', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/gv%27s-heating-%26-cooling', E'Consumer Services', E'🏠💨🌟
HVAC | Home Air Quality | Family Culture

Creating an oasis of fresh air and exceptional air quality, GV''S Heating and Cooling has been serving the North Shore since 1990. Founded by Greg and Pam Vickers, our company focuses on delivering superior HVAC solutions while prioritizing the wellbeing of families.

🔧🌡️⚙️
Join a team that embraces innovation, values relationships, and strives for excellence. At GV''S Heating and Cooling, we welcome passionate thinkers and doers who align with our core values of Respect, Heart-felt Caring, Integrity, and Passion. Together, we prioritize Health, Safety, Comfort, and Efficiency for our customers.

💪🌬️🌴
Experience a work environment that feels like family. Our company culture fosters a familial atmosphere, ensuring everyone feels connected and supported. We embrace change and continuously seek opportunities to improve our business and deliver the best heating, air conditioning, and indoor air quality solutions.

