Established in 2014, The Roof Clinic is a Georgia-based roofing contractor specializing in private and governmental contracting within commercial roofing as well as residential roofing repair and replacement. Our team offers expertise in a variety of roofing services and prioritizes quality craftsmanship and timeliness. Our focus is to handle every interaction with the utmost integrity. 

Collectively the company holds over 20 years of roofing and general construction background. We know and LOVE roofing. 

Our focus is to meet every project deadline and minimize if not eliminate business interruption so that business owners can continue doing what they do best - serving the community. It is crucial that The Roof Clinic team maintain the knowledge base to recommend the best repair/replacement practices needed for each project. This is the reason all personnel complete ongoing field base training to ensure our workmanship, customer interaction and products are ahead of the curve and keeping with new age technology and roofing scope practices.', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''shingle services'', ''gutter cleaning'', ''roof leak repair'', ''roof sealing'', ''roof maintenance'', ''skylight installation &replacmeent'', ''gutter repair'', ''tpo roofs'', ''metal roofs'', ''roof cleaning'', ''flat roofs'', ''roofing'', ''gutters'', ''siding'', ''residential roofing replacement'', ''commercial roofing replacement'', ''roofing repair'', ''emergency services'', ''roof leak detection'', ''insurance claims'', ''roof estimate'', ''replacement'', ''commercial'', ''installation'', ''repair'', ''construction'', ''residential'']', E'https://www.theroofclinic.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Sugar Hill, GA, United States', E'Sugar Hill', E'Georgia', E'United States', E'[''678-765-2992'', ''2147483647'', ''+1 678 765 2992'']', E'[''info@theroofclinic.com'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/theroofclinic', E'https://www.twitter.com/theroofclinic', NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/theroofclinic', E'3002660'),
