ng and serving your needs with open communication, meeting your deadlines and follow through to ensure project satisfaction.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/signature-innovations-llc', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'Signature Innovations, LLC d.b.a SIGNATURE HARDWOODS™ is Chicagoland’s premier custom designer, manufacturer and installer of true European bespoke hand-scraped and antiqued hardwood flooring—recognized worldwide for creating beautiful and enduring floor designs. 

