Established in 2002 with the goal of introducing innovative products using advanced technology, Signature has undoubtedly mastered the art of custom hardwood flooring. Signature is the place for true professionals, designers, architects and builders searching for an exquisite and distinctive design. We cater to those who expect products and service that are unsurpassed by any others in the industry. 

You may ask what sets our company and products apart from other luxury hardwood floor suppliers. Simply put, it is our insistence on using only the finest woods and the most talented European craftsmen, while always maintaining careful awareness for the environment and a dedication to the art and tradition of creating beautiful, enduring floors. It is only at Signature that your feet will find the comfort of such a thoughtfully chosen selection, masterfully worked to last the test of time, for you and your future generations.

Standing by our reputation for thoroughly satisfying even the most discriminating clients, we welcome any design challenge. With every project, the Signature service guarantees you our persistent demand for perfection, our passionate attention to details and the benefits of our ever progressing innovation. We pride ourselves in being a leading authority in the fine hardwood industry, in regards to both products and installation.', E'[''manufacturing'', ''custom hardwood flooring'', ''handcrafted wood beams & mantels'', ''sound control subfloor underlayments'', ''speciatly floor adhesives & primers'', ''wood finishing products'', ''dutch made moisture resistant engineered hardwood flooring'', ''sugar'', ''testing'', ''inspection'', ''oil and gas'']', E'https://www.signatureinnovations.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Elk Grove Village, Illinois, United States', E'Elk Grove Village', E'Illinois', E'United States', E'[''847.758.9600'']', E'[''sales@signaturehardwoods.com'']', E'[''houzz'', ''elk'', ''amp'', ''square'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/signatureinnovations', NULL, NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/signaturehardwoods', NULL),
