  (E'Kyle', E'Fisher', E'Controller', E'Rountree Glass Co', NULL, E'kyle@rountreeglass.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Los Angeles, California, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Finance & Accounting', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/kyleifisher', E'My range stretches from project management to graphic design, from accounting to video editing. Between Hospitality Services, Construction, Indoor Entertainment, and TV & Film, I have over 7 years experience in various forms of accounting. Along the way I have mixed those skills with experiences in Marketing, IT, and Product Management to develop a diverse and useful set of interconnected skills. For 2 years I also served as the Master of Ceremonies for the annual Sky Zone International Convention for 500+ employees and franchisees, along with their biannual all-hands meetings. My latest project required my design, IT, accounting, and strategy skills to successfully convert 150+ domestic franchise Sky Zone indoor parks to a modern gift card platform, while managing a cross-departmental team of 15 people. This conversion led to a 12% growth in gift card sales while the overall year-over-year sales for the network had a 6% decline. Since then I have been fully self-employed working as a handyman, personal assistant, and artist. I have found that whatever problem I face can be resolved, and I look forward to doing my diligence to uncover the most efficient and long lasting resolutions for those problems. I like to see where the cracks are and how to fill and improve them.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/rountree-glass-co', E'Construction', NULL, E'[''construction/building materials'', ''specialty glass'', ''commercial windows'', ''commercial glass installation'', ''commercial hardware'', ''fire rated glazing'']', E'https://www.rountreeglass.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Glendale, California, United States', E'Glendale', E'California', E'United States', E'[''(818) 246 1785'']', E