  (E'Raymond', E'Jenkins', E'Marketing Lead — TriVAN Roofing', E'TriVAN Roofing', NULL, E'raymond.jenkins@trivanroofing.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Keller, Texas, United States', E'United States', E'Owner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/raymondjenkins1', E'As the Marketing Lead at TriVAN Roofing, I focus on building a powerful and consistent digital presence that drives brand growth, lead generation, and industry authority across Texas and Oklahoma. With a background in full-stack web development, SEO, and high-performance digital strategy, I bring a technical and creative approach to commercial roofing marketing.

My work blends strategic planning, data analytics, and hands-on execution. I develop content that educates commercial property owners and decision-makers, manage digital advertising and SEO campaigns, build conversion-focused landing pages, and create processes that strengthen TriVAN’s visibility in the market. I collaborate closely with our operations and sales teams to ensure every marketing initiative has clear business impact.

I’m passionate about scaling service-based brands, leveraging modern tools and automation, and creating digital ecosystems that convert consistently and sustainably.

If you’re in the roofing, construction, or building management sector — or if you’re passionate about digital marketing and growth strategy — I’d love to connect.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/trivan-roofing-%26-construction', E'Construction', E'Sherry and Dave Custable formed TriVAN in 2001 with the goal of providing a stable future for their three children. Emphasis on family is deeply rooted in TriVAN''s history and is evidenced by the company name itself, Tri meaning three (Vanessa, Anthony, Nicholette). Our purpose is to operate as a family business that adds honesty and integrity to an industry sorely lacking in both. We aim to be more than just a faceless corporation fixated on the bottom line; we understand that roofing is about protection and we provide peace of mind by only working with the best materials and professionals. To that end we have persistently sought self improvement. TriVAN is licensed by the Roofing Contractors Association of Texas (RCAT) and Endorsed by the CIB for Commercial Roofing in Oklahoma. TriVAN has established itself as a commercial Elite Certified Contractor with Duro-Last PVC roof systems, and as a residential GAF Shingle Manufacturer Master Elite (License #ME21251). The emphasis on customer safety and satisfaction from every single one of our committed team members is the reason why TriVAN has an A+ rating with the Better Business Bureau. 98% of our multi-million dollar revenue base is from customer referrals, which we believe to be representative of our mission. 

Please contact us today for a free inspection or to answer any of your roofing questions. 

