  (E'Timothy', E'Davidson', E'Owner/Senior Consultant', E'Derby Overhead Company', NULL, E'tim@derbyoverhead.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Derby, Kansas, United States', E'United States', E'Owner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/timothy-davidson-82787b69', E'Over 35 years in the garage door industry. You could say I started as a boy hanging out at a place called Roberts Overdoors in Derby, Kansas with my father, earning a quarter a night picking up screws, and bolts in the driveway. About 1983 my father started a new, and used garage door company, right behind Roberts. Well nights, and weekends were now gone, for at the ripe old age of 16 I was now starting a career as a garage door tech. At 22 I went to work for Roberts for about a year and a half and still worked for dad nights, and weekends. I feel cursed, and blessed everyday for the knowledge I have for overhead doors. I can solve, or fix most all issues that arise. What I love to sell most is value. and I am not talking dollars, and cents. What I am selling to the customer is my integrity, the doors follow me. I have a drive to always give 110% at everything. Sales is a passion not just a career. When I started at Overhead Door Company, I boosted over the counter sales by over 500%, within a 5 month period by simply starting a wholesale aspect. As a Manager I try my best to learn something new everyday, for in a innovative world, you must research the good, and bad ideas of tomorrow, outweigh the pros and cons and implement them if needed. I am with a company now that I helped start growing in 2017, it is Derby Overhead Company and I will Take it to the Top, for building business is what I do best.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/derby-overhead-company', E'Construction', E'With owners Greg Hayden and Tim Davidson having more than 60 years of experience in the industry and Donny Sechrist’s business acumen, Derby Overhead Company is your garage door solution company.

From broken springs to installing a new garage door, our skilled technicians can fix, replace or install what you need.
We repair, service and install 
•	Residential garage doors and openers
•	Canister doors
•	Rolling steel doors
•	Commercial sectional doors and openers
•	Docks and dock levelers
We are also your local dealer for Beam Central Vacuums.', E'[''home services'', ''upgrades'', ''wichita area'', ''replacements'', ''garage door repairs'', ''customer service'']', E'https://www.derbyoverhead.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Derby, KS, United States', E'Derby', E'Kansas', E'United States', E'[''(316) 788-8889'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/derbyoverhead', NULL, E'https://www.youtube.com/channel/uc3_x5o5mdzqkftmhxip9veg', E'https://www.instagram.com/derbyoverheadcompany', NULL),
