  (E'Philippe', E'Bishop', E'Partner', E'Alpenfire Cider', NULL, E'philippe@nwcider.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Greater Seattle Area United States', E'United States', E'Partner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/philippe-bishop-2702885', E'Experienced Photographer with a demonstrated history of working in the wine and spirits industry. Strong arts and design professional skilled in Photography, Beverage Industry, Sales, Adobe Creative Suite, and Graphic Design.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alpenfire-cider', E'Food and Beverage Services', E'Alpenfire''s ciders range in style from old world to new world; from barrel matured, bittersharp, bone dry varieties to luscious pommeau''s made with fresh pressed juice and apple brandy. 

