  (E'Austin', E'Noah', E'Service Manager/ Project Manager', E'Texan Water', NULL, E'anoah@texanwater.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'New Braunfels, Texas, United States', E'United States', E'Manager', E'Project Management', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/austin-noah-5a7bb976', NULL, E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/texan-water', E'Consumer Services', E'Welcome to Texan Water. We are a full-service water well drilling company specializing in water well drilling, well service & repair, water storage, well plugging and abandonment, inspections and low water-yield solutions. We are based out of Central Texas and the Hill Country with locations in Marble Falls, Dripping Springs, Spring Branch & Lampasas. 

