  (E'Joshua', E'Kosova', E'Business Owner', E'Indoor Climate Experts HVAC', NULL, E'josh@ice-hvac.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Greater Chicago Area United States', E'United States', E'Owner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/icehvac', E'Experienced Heating and Air Conditioning Technician with a Focus in Indoor Air Quality. Entrepreneur with commitment to balance profit and philanthropic services. Former Service Advisor with a demonstrated history of working in the automotive industry. Skilled in Emergency Vehicle Customizations, Account Management, Direct Sales, Strategic Planning, and Leadership. Strong support professional with a Associate''s degree focused in Engineering from Harper College.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/indoorclimateexpertshvac', E'Consumer Services', E'Indoor Climate Experts HVAC is a locally owned heating and air conditioning business that services Barrington and the surrounding area. Our team is dedicated to providing the local community with trusted advisers, honest technicians and quality comfort solutions.
Our NATE certified technicians offer quality service & Installations on; high-efficient heating & air-conditioning, fresh air ventilation, duct-work, home humidification control systems and a variety of holistic air purification systems.

We are driven to provide you with industry leading expertise that insures each job done properly the first time. Our highly skilled team is motivated to exceed our clients expectations in providing quality and efficiency.
We are firm believers that, "your equipment will only last as well as it''s installed, tuned and maintained."
At ICEHVAC, we understand the importance of providing careful consideration in respect to each and every aspect of our projects. This allows us to guarantee that upon our departure, you will be feeling healthier, confident and satisfied with our services.
What is IAQ?
We are dedicated to educate our community in regards to the importance of indoor air quality and its effect on their health and our environment. Clients seek our services based on our quality of work and our unique knowledge of the emerging Indoor Air Quality (IAQ) market.
Want Carefree Comfort?
Our company offers smart home integrated Lennox HVAC equipment that allows us to provide 24 hour HVAC diagnostics & monitoring. In addition, we promote the use of ultra-high efficient heating & air conditioning equipment to decrease their carbon footprint while saving money.
Charitable Services
We strive to make a positive impact in our community through charitable contributions to various local & national charitable organizations. As our business grows, so will our ability to help those in need. We are always accepting requests for donations so please submit your requests.', E'[''hvac'', ''indoor air quality'', ''smart home integration'', ''premier lennox dealer'', ''high efficiency'', ''air conditioning'', ''heating'', ''ventilation'', ''ultra smart thermostats'', ''uv filter'', ''humidification'', ''air filters'', ''clean room'', ''ductwork'', ''water heaters'', ''philathropy'', ''air purification'', ''consulting'', ''ionization'', ''furnace'', ''heat pump'', ''air handler'', ''boiler'', ''radiant'', ''quality'', ''efficiency tuning'', ''tune-up'', ''energy efficiency'', ''commercial'', ''maintenance'', ''residential'']', E'https://www.ice-hvac.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Barrington, Illinois, United States', E'Barrington', E'Illinois', E'United States', E'[''(847) 302-0071'']', NULL, E'[''recognize'', ''well'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/indoorclimateexpertshvacllc', E'https://www.twitter.com/ice_barrington?s=03', NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/indoorclimateexpertshvac', NULL),
