Sustainable Solution
The Cost-Efficient Alternative to Tear-Off/Reroof
Specific, Customizable Warranties up to 25 Years
Commercial and Industrial Restoration

Alaska Roof Restorations offers a proactive roofing solution as opposed to the ''old-school'' mentality of tearing off roofs. We specialize in cost-efficient restoration of existing flat roof, low slope & metal roofs. We are the responsible roofing solution that saves you money by installing a lower cost system that will also save significant sums of money over the life of the building by eliminating the need to ever have to tear off and replace a roof. Additionally, our systems are renewable for the life of the building, creating a sustainable roof solution with a renewable warranty. Our seamless membrane options are applied directly on top of the existing roof material and will last for the life of the building when properly maintained. Once the new fluid applied roof membrane is approaching the end of it''s useful life, our warranties are renewed by simply applying an additional layer of top coat on top of the initial coating. Meet sustainability goals, save money and never tear off your roof again!', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''commercial roofing'', ''flat roof repair'', ''flat roof maintenance'', ''flat roof inspection'', ''roof restoration'', ''flat roofs'', ''low slope roofs'', ''metal roofs'', ''renewable alternatives'']', E'https://www.alaskaroofrestorations.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Anchorage, AK, United States', E'Anchorage', E'Alaska', E'United States', E'[''903-1190'', ''(907) 903-1190'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/alaskaroofrestorations', NULL, NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/alaskaroofrestorations', NULL),
