  (E'William', E'Cotter', E'General Manager', E'Signature Roofing Inc', NULL, E'william@signatureroofing.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'San Jose, California, United States', E'United States', E'Manager', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/william-cotter-0aa4ab23', E'18+ years of operational and management roles in military, non-profit and residential construction sectors. Proud United States Air Force Security Forces Veteran. Significant involvement in startup of a 501(c)(3) non-profit organization now encompassing the majority of California supporting over 80+ facilities and organizations. Instrumental in steady growth of residential roofing company; increased sales goals from average $2.5M/per year to average $5.5M/per year within 3-1/2 years. Responsible for hiring and training new personnel to align with steady growth. Identified opportunities to increase presence in market while maintaining high level of quality control and client satisfaction. Responsible for day to day operations of production and maintaining continued pipeline.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/signature-roofing-inc', E'Construction', E'29+ years in residential re-roofing, specializing in asphalt shingles roofs. 

Established in 1993.

Everything About Us is an Open Book.

Signature Roofing has been in business for over 25 years. Our certified roofing crews have installed nearly 5,000 roofs across San Mateo and Santa Clara counties. Feel free to check our ratings, our licenses and our proofs of insurance. A reputable roofing company has nothing to hide.
About us:
 * We carry $2M in liability insurance and required Workers'' Comp
 * We are state licensed in good standing with a complaint-free record
 * We hold a valid business license in your city
 * We obtain building permits and schedule city inspections
 * City building inspectors know and respect our work
 * We follow all city building codes and work hour regulations
 * Better Business Bureau''s A+ rating since 1993

A Local Roofing Company That Does Roofing a Little Differently

Business Owner George Belden, founded Signature Roofing in 1993. If you''re lucky, you''ll see or hear from a roofing company''s owner once, usually never. That''s not how we do things here. After all these years George still personally supervises the scheduling of each project and oversees the operations of each job. His Assistant General Manager William Cotter overseas all quotes. Our trained crews are company employees with us for a decade or more, not strangers - we don''t subcontract roofers.

Signature Roofing is one of the few San Mateo and Santa Clara county roofing companies that:

* Never files pre-lien notices on your home
