  (E'Rusty', E'Dillon', E'Custom Tile Sales', E'Villa Lagoon Tile', NULL, E'rusty@villalagoontile.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Foley, Alabama, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Sales', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/rusty-dillon-a9620a121', E'I have worn many hats in the past from very technical, highly trained occupations to more laid back customer service-oriented occupations. I have experience in many aspects of business ownership and management including scheduling, organization, networking, marketing, and promoting. I seldom meet strangers and believe a positive attitude while conducting business is essential. I''m not afraid to laugh and kid around with clients when appropriate. I have been in the position, and am comfortable working with clients on sales well over 10''s of thousands of dollars. I don''t get nervous in these situations as I have been fortunate enough sell products that I strongly believe in. In fact, I have put a lot of effort into assuring that I am not in the position of having to sell something I don''t believe in. I have worked with many people from around the globe and always find it interesting and fun working with people from other cultures. I enjoy putting effort into learning customs and social interaction protocols. I am, unfortunately, terrible at learning other languages, though. My passions range greatly, with a few major core themes. Music has been a large part of my life, although, never professionally (except for installing sound systems into cars). But I have been banging around on drums since I was a very little kid, so I can drop a beat on just about any melody. I love woodworking and consider myself an avid and fairly accomplished woodworker. Electronics have always intrigued me as well. A current obsession for me has been learning to program and build with Arduino boards. Art and design has also been an area of interest- at least the admiration of...', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/villa-lagoon-tile', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'Villa Lagoon Tile is the premier distributor of encaustic cement tile both domestically and globally. Cement Tile is known globally by many names, Cuban tile, Moroccan tile, Mission Tile, and Mosaicos Hidraulicos to name a few.

