  (E'John', E'Adams', E'Director of Technology and Supply Chain Management', E'Villa Lagoon Tile', NULL, E'john@villalagoontile.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Bon Secour, Alabama, United States', E'United States', E'Director', E'Engineering and Technical', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/john-m-adams', E'I currently serve as Director of Technology at Villa Lagoon Tile, which has been my title for most of my 10 year tenure. We produce and sell the most beautiful hand crafted tiles and decorative breeze blocks in the world. I provide support to our entire organization, managing our ERP/CMS, data stores, and logistics infrastructure. I author technical documents, product descriptions, and produce miscellaneous graphics. I have even created or co-created some of our best selling tile patterns, and created a web application for designing and visualizing our tiles in custom colors, which can be found at https://www.villalagoontile.com/tile-design-tool/', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/villa-lagoon-tile', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'Villa Lagoon Tile is the premier distributor of encaustic cement tile both domestically and globally. Cement Tile is known globally by many names, Cuban tile, Moroccan tile, Mission Tile, and Mosaicos Hidraulicos to name a few.

Every cement tile is a hand-crafted work of art, with patterns formed by arranging mineral-pigmented cement blends in a mold, before being subjected to a hydraulic press and set to cure. Villa Lagoon Tile sources only the finest of these tiles through manufacturing partnerships in Vietnam, Mexico, the Caribbean, and Morocco.

Villa Lagoon Tile serves in-stock cement tile through its warehouse at the home office in Gulf Shores, AL, and ships custom tile throughout the world, including Europe, Asia, and Australia. Villa Lagoon Tile also provides custom tile creation with limitless possibilities, and hundreds of standard and exclusive patterns.', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''cement tile'', ''cuban tile'', ''encaustic tile'', ''mosaicos hidraulicos'', ''moroccan tile'', ''custom tile'', ''bespoke tile'', ''encaustic cement tile'', ''mission tile'', ''spanish tile'', ''french tile'', ''geometric tile'', ''designer tile'', ''hand-made tile'', ''high-end tile'', ''luxury tile'', ''hospitality design'', ''interior design'', ''residential design'', ''international logistics'', ''cement tiles'', ''encaustic cement tiles'', ''in-stock'', ''flexibility'', ''custom'', ''building material'', ''manufacturing'', ''wholesale'']', E'https://www.villalagoontile.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Gulf Shores, Alabama, United States', E'Gulf Shores', E'Alabama', E'United States', E'[''1-251-968-3375'', ''+1 251-968-3375'', ''2008-2024'']', E'[''info@villalagoontile.com'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/villalagoontile/?ref=page_internal', E'https://www.twitter.com/villalagoontile', E'https://www.youtube.com/user/villalagoontile', E'https://www.instagram.com/villalagoontile', E'368152'),
