  (E'Charlotte', E'Williams', E'Operations Manager', E'ACTexas', NULL, E'charlotte@actexas.us', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Spring, Texas, United States', E'United States', E'Manager', E'Operations', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/charlotte-williams-6a2609267', E'I am currently a student at Sam Houston State University pursuing my Bachelors of Business Administration where I am projected to graduate May of 2024. During my academic career I’ve been able to balance school work and a managerial position at ACTexas Cooling and Heating. Throughout my three years at ACTexas, I have risen to the position of Office Manager. Through this I have learned how to efficiently manage a team, navigate stressful situations and successfully resolve conflict in the workplace. As a Business Professional I always strive to create a positive work environment and impact on my coworkers. I always implement fun games and challenges throughout the work week to motivate and boost morale in my office. I display a high level of integrity and I am dedicated to continuously grow and develop my skills while building strong connections. I always make a point to provide great customer service while exceeding their expectations in order build relationships with my customers.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ac-texas07', E'Consumer Services', E'ACTexas Air Conditioning will provide quality products and services to the highest standards of our industry, on time, every time. We always keep the best interests of our clients in mind, and your comfort is our priority. We will always strive for professionalism and peace of mind to be the only HVAC company you call when you need HVAC maintenance or repairs. We handle every service call as an opportunity to earn your trust and your business. Some of our top priorities include attention to detail with superior craftsmanship and reliable service you can count on time and again. Our goal is to deliver nothing but the highest quality at the best price possible. We hold ourselves to a higher standard and operate day to day by the core values and philosophies that set our team apart. Simply put, our clients are our number one priority, always. We won’t be satisfied unless our clients are, too. 

We’re more than just a local business—we’re your neighbors! We’re proud to serve the communities we live in, and we approach each job as our own way of making the world around us just a little bit better for everyone. It’s this same motivation that has pushed us to strive for excellence with every job we’ve taken since our very first day in business.', E'[''hvac'', ''commercial'', ''heating'', ''residential'', ''air conditioning'', ''customer service'', ''ventilation'', ''and air conditioning (hvac)'', ''mechanical engineering'']', E'https://www.actexas.us', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'The Woodlands, Texas, United States', E'The Woodlands', E'Texas', E'United States', E'[''(281) 355-1500'', ''+1 281-355-1500'']', E'[''service@actexas.us'']', E'[''facebook'', ''instagram'', ''google my business'', ''canva'', ''hootsuite'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/actexasairconditioningheating', E'https://www.twitter.com/act_ac_tx', NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/actexas_hvac', NULL),
