  (E'Mike', E'Kramer', E'President', E'Metal Monsters, Inc.', NULL, E'mike@metalmonstersinc.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'North Liberty, Iowa, United States', E'United States', E'President/Vice President', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/mike-kramer-a3a45177', NULL, E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/metal-monsters-inc.', E'Construction', NULL, E'[''permanent'', ''energy-efficient'', ''roof systems'', ''residential'', ''gutter systems'', ''construction/building materials'', ''industry: n/a'']', E'https://www.metalmonstersinc.com', NULL, NULL, E'North Liberty, Iowa, United States', E'North Liberty', E'Iowa', E'United States', E'[''(319) 665-2024'', ''319-665-2024'']', E'[''sales@metalmonstersinc.com'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/metalmonstersinc', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'7132789'),
  (E'Reese', E'Arrington', E'Sales Specialist', E'Arrington Roofing Co., Inc', NULL, E'reese@arringtonroofing.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Dallas, Texas, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Sales', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/reese-arrington-88a011183', E'"All the worlds a stage, and all the men and women merely players" - William Shakespeare Performing lit a fire within me. I love telling a good story. Whether I''m acting in a short film or selling a product or service, there is a story to be told. The beginning always starts with a person with a problem, followed by attempts to escape it, failures to do so, then finally discovering a solution that works. No matter where I enter, my goal is to help clients see themselves as the hero of their own story. Framing myself or the brand not as the savior, but as the guide or tool that leads them to their own victory. I started my sales journey in the roofing industry. My father started and owns a successful roofing company in Dallas, TX where I started working almost immediately after graduating college with an oh-so-versatile Fine-Arts Acting degree. I am incredibly proud of this degree, as it was a highly competitive program for which thousands applied and only 14 were accepted. I quickly found that the communication skills, collaborative training, and performance techniques I learned in acting classes were paramount to any product knowledge I had mastered from being raised in the industry. At the end of the day, people want to be heard and valued. Listening is one of the most important aspects of performance, and I soon found the same to be true of sales. In order to form a solution, it''s crucial to understand the problem. It''s typical for actors and performers to live and think abstractly, but my approach to performance has been one of deep analytics. I can sometimes become obsessed with the question, "why?" I avoid the pits of existential crisis this thinking can lead to, and rather use it as a means to understand motivation. Why do people do what they do? The human condition has always fascinated me, it is as surprising as it is elusive. Being human myself, completely understanding people is impossible, which makes it just that much more fun to try to figure out. It''s a true journey, and I''ve learned to delight in the process.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/arrington-roofing-co.-inc', E'Construction', E'With degreed backgrounds in architecture, the Arrington team has a unique combination of an eye for design with a mind for construction. We recognize that the roofing industry lacks regulation and controlled standards leaving a tainted reputation in the minds of consumers. Most roofers have access to the same materials. It is our skill and talent in designing and constructing a roof system that sets us apart. At Arrington, we bring a whole new level of knowledge and expertise to each job.

Arrington is a full service roofing and energy solutions company serving residential and commercial clients in the greater Dallas area since 1983. Founder, Chris Arrington, built the company based on his passion for solving problems and his genuine desire to serve and help people.', E'[''roof repairs'', ''roof replacements'', ''attic ventilation'', ''flat roofs'', ''construction/building materials'', ''siding'', ''gutters'', ''roofing'', ''commercial'', ''residential'']', E'https://www.arringtonroofing.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Dallas, TX, United States', E'Dallas', E'Texas', E'United States', E'[''214-698-8443'', ''(214) 817-3274'', ''214-817-3274'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/arringtonroofing', E'https://www.twitter.com/arringtonroofin', NULL, NULL, E'885494'),
