  (E'Amy', E'Hallem', E'Marketing Manager', E'Foss Security', NULL, E'ahallem@fosssecurity.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Sioux Falls, South Dakota, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Design', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/amy-hallem-90ab52b1', E'I’m a designer with a marketing brain — currently working as a marketing manager while also offering freelance design and strategy services. I bring 15+ years of experience across print, branding, and creative direction, and love helping clients find clarity through design that actually supports their goals. If you’re a small team, startup, or marketer looking for someone who gets both messaging and visuals, I’d love to connect. Always happy to chat about creative collaborations, freelance opportunities, or sharing ideas.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/foss-avi', E'Security Systems Services', E'At FOSS, we believe that security is not just about technology—it''s about creating a circle of trust that binds communities together. As a Sioux Falls native company, we''ve dedicated over two decades to protecting and serving our neighbors, not just as customers, but as an extended family. Our mission is to build trust and exceed expectations within our local community, ensuring that every household and business feels safe, respected, and valued.

What sets FOSS apart is not just our experience, but our commitment to understanding and fulfilling the unique needs of each client. We don''t believe in one-size-fits-all solutions. Instead, we engage with each customer, understanding their concerns and aspirations, and then tailor our services to fit those specific needs. Our team of seasoned professionals brings a blend of rich experience and innovative spirit to each project, ensuring that every solution is not just effective but also forward-thinking.

Our service portfolio includes:
Residential Security: Ensuring the safety of your home and loved ones with state-of-the-art security systems, cameras, and home management solutions.
Commercial Security: Protecting your business with robust security measures, including advanced camera systems, access control, and fire alarms.
Custom Solutions: Understanding that each client is unique, we offer custom solutions designed to meet the specific demands of your home or business.
At FOSS, we believe that every interaction is personal, every project is pivotal, and every customer is a relationship worth nurturing. Our approach goes beyond meeting sales targets; it''s about building lasting relationships based on trust, reliability, and unparalleled service.

For inquiries, collaborations, or to learn more about how we can tailor our solutions to your needs, feel free to reach out. Let''s make Sioux Falls not just a place to live, but a secure, thriving community for all.

#FOSSSecurity #CommunityFirst #InnovativeSolutions', E'[''security'', ''security/alarm systems'', ''camera systems'', ''access systems'', ''temperature control & monitoring'', ''light & lock control'', ''voice'', ''data'', ''& fiber optic cabiling'', ''automation systems'', ''telephone systems'', ''central vacuums'', ''alarm systems'', ''technology'', ''connectivity'', ''home management'', ''field support'', ''home services'']', E'https://www.fosssecurity.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Sioux Falls, SD, United States', E'Sioux Falls', E'South Dakota', E'United States', E'[''+1 605 339 0575'', ''(605)339.0575'', ''605-339-0575'']', E'[''info@fosssecurity.com'']', E'[''well'', ''amp'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/fosssd', E'https://www.twitter.com/fosssecurity', E'https://www.youtube.com/@fosssecurity5451', E'https://www.instagram.com/fosssecuritysd', NULL),
