  (E'Buffi', E'Stanley', E'Business Owner', E'AMI Roofing', NULL, E'buffi@amiroof.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Jasper, Georgia, United States', E'United States', E'Owner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/buffi-stanley-72aaa532', NULL, E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ami-roofing', E'Construction', E'AMI Roofing has been serving North GA and the Cherokee County Area for many years. We are known for our high level of professionalism, years of experience, and dedication to customer service. We pride ourselves in our quality control of every project that we take on. You won’t get any better installation than with AMI Roofing and we are so sure of this that we offer a 3-5 Year Workmanship Warranty.', E'[''construction/building materials'', ''gutter guards'', ''commercial'', ''residential'', ''gutters'', ''roofing'']', E'https://www.amiroof.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Jasper, GA, United States', E'Jasper', E'Georgia', E'United States', E'[''(770) 345-3000'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/amiroofing', NULL, NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/amiroofing', NULL),
  (E'Eric', E'Trybala', E'Owner', E'Tri-Tex Roof Systems', NULL, E'erict@tritexroofing.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Liberty Hill, Texas, United States', E'United States', E'Owner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/eric-trybala-6652b1322', E'With a background in insurance, mortgage, and real estate, I’ve spent my career helping people make informed decisions about their most valuable assets. I understand the financial and logistical challenges that property owners and managers face when it comes to maintaining their buildings—and I also know how complex the insurance and claims process can be after a storm. That’s why at Tri-Tex Roof Systems, I take a consultative approach to roofing. My focus isn’t just on fixing or replacing a roof—it’s on helping clients protect their properties, understand their options, and make the most strategic decisions possible. Whether you’re navigating an insurance claim, planning for preventative roof maintenance, or simply trying to extend the life of your investment, I’m here to help. At Tri-Tex, we specialize in: -Storm Restoration &amp; Insurance Collaboration Assistance – Helping property owners understand their coverage, work within insurance guidelines, and maximize their claims without unnecessary stress. -Commercial &amp; Residential Roofing – Providing customized solutions that align with both property needs and budget realities. -Preventative Maintenance Plans – Helping property managers and commercial building owners avoid costly repairs through regular roof assessments and preventative care. Why Work With Me? My experience across real estate, mortgage, and insurance allows me to bridge the gap between roofing, finance, and claims processes—giving my clients a competitive edge in protecting their properties. Outside of work, I enjoy spending time with my wife and kids, playing guitar, and making the most of life’s everyday moments. Let’s connect! If you’re a property owner, manager, or industry professional looking for insights into roofing, insurance claims, or preventative maintenance, I’m happy to help.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tri-tex-roof-systems', E'Construction', E'Tri-Tex Roof Systems is a trusted Central Texas roofing and storm restoration company serving residential, commercial, and new construction clients since 2008.

Backed by deep expertise in roofing, insurance, mortgage, and real estate, we bring insight and care to every project—from first inspection to final walk-through.

We specialize in:
🔹 Commercial roofing: proactive inspections, capital planning, system replacements
🔹 Residential storm restoration: documentation, insurance guidance, peace of mind
🔹 New construction roofing: reliable installs, builder coordination, long-term performance

Our commercial division supports property managers, facility directors, ownership groups, and builders with transparent timelines, seasoned crews, and long-term roof protection strategies.

What sets us apart: 
✔️ We help you understand your roof’s risk before the storm
✔️ We guide you through the claims process with speed and clarity
✔️ We deliver dependable results—with zero pressure, always

Tri-Tex is proud to partner with realtors, adjusters, builders, and commercial decision-makers across Central Texas.

