  (E'Anthony', E'Weidner', E'Owner/Operator', E'Don''s Appliances', NULL, E'anthony@donsappliancessocal.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Signal Hill, California, United States', E'United States', E'Owner', E'C-Suite', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/anthony-weidner-03416886', E'Don’s Appliances has been successfully serving the families of the greater Long beach area for over 30 years. After original owner, Don Muldoon, passed away about a decade ago, he passed the torch to his Grandson. Since then, Anthony Weidner has kept his Grandfather’s legacy alive and continues to deliver honest, personal, sincere service when it comes to your home appliances. In these ever evolving technological times, Don’s Appliances continues to be a leader in the Appliance Service Industry not only by continuing technical training, but also having fundamental values that go back to the beginning of time. We are real people, working with real people problems!', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/donsappliances', E'Consumer Services', E'Don’s Appliances continues to be a leader in the Appliance Service Industry not only by continuing technical training, but also having fundamental values that go back to the beginning of time. We are real people, working with real people problems! Don’s Appliances has been successfully serving the families of the greater Long beach area for over 40 years.', E'[''legal services'', ''law firm'', ''construction and architecture law'', ''migration law'', ''administrative law'', ''family law'']', E'https://www.donsappliancessocal.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Long Beach , CA, United States', E'Long Beach Area Long Beach', E'California', E'United States', E'[''(562) 437-6666'', ''951) 529-7870'', ''562-437-6666'', ''951-529-7870'']', E'[''service@donsappliancessocal.com'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/donsappliancessocal', NULL, NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/donsappliances', NULL),
  (E'Holly', E'Mills', E'Dispatcher', E'Pioneer Heating, Cooling, Plumbing & Electrical', NULL, E'holly.mills@pioneercomfort.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Corryton, Tennessee, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Administrative', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/holly-mills-20a94b290', E'My name is Holly Mills, I currently reside in the beautiful small town of Corryton. When I was in High school I didn’t know what I wanted to do. Right after graduation I got a job at the Pilot gas station about 10 minutes from my dads house. It started out as a job as a cashier just a Monday-Friday job. I didn’t know it would be that job that showed me that I was able to advance and become more than just a cashier. I started working my way up and then achieving an assistant management before the age of 21. I eventually decided to leave due to some family members having serious health issues and needed help. I became a bartender for a short period of time at nights to help make a little extra money. I didn’t know I would soon be starting a family of my own. After I had my little girl I got a job in a “call center” starting as a customer service representative, advanced to the retail department within my first year, getting everything flat and stable. After that I advanced to inside sales, not knowing in a few months I would become the lead dispatcher. I strive everyday to make sure that my family comes first, but not only that, to be better today than I was yesterday. I take pride in everything that I do and I want to accomplish my goal of growing and becoming more successful.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/frog-heating-air-electrical', E'HVAC and Refrigeration Equipment Manufacturing', E'Pioneer Heating, Cooling, Plumbing & Electrical is setting the standard for home comfort in Nashville and the surrounding communities. Specializing in heating, cooling, indoor air quality, electrical and plumbing services, our team provides responsive, dependable HVAC and electrical expertise with the best service and price in the region.', E'[''home services'', ''heating'', ''air conditioning'', ''electrical'', ''ventilation'', ''plumbing'', ''electrical services'', ''drain'', ''hvac'', ''nashville'', ''real-estate-construction'', ''construction-design'', ''air-conditioning'', ''customer service'', ''and air conditioning (hvac)'', ''residential'']', E'https://www.pioneercomfort.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Nashville, Tennessee, United States', E'Nashville', E'Tennessee', E'United States', E'[''2224145'', ''+1 865 922 2817'', ''2208210'', ''2243229'', ''(615) 205-5364'']', E'[''info@pioneercomfort.com'']', E'[''microsoft office'', ''microsoft'', ''well'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/pioneerheatingandair', E'https://www.twitter.com/pioneercomfort', E'https://www.youtube.com/@pioneerheatingaircondition6616', E'https://www.instagram.com/pioneercomfort_', E'7942845'),
  (E'Rick', E'Bond', E'International Sales Consultant', E'Southern Advantage Company, Inc.', NULL, E'rick@soadv.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Huntersville, North Carolina, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Sales', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/rick-bond-400b9847', NULL, E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/southern-advantage-company-inc-', E'Retail', E'Specializing in professional & broadcast video equipment since 1996, we’ve spent the last 15 years proudly offering consumers “The Southern Advantage!” You might be wondering to yourself what exactly that means. The answer is easy: slowing down.

The south has always been known for its hospitality and its laid back attitude. Here at Southern Advantage, we don’t mind being accused of that.

From the chair of the CEO to the customer service representatives, from our highly trained technicians to the employees in our warehouse and everywhere in between, we all have one goal in common here at Southern Advantage; slowing down enough to serve you. 

Slowing down enough to hear your needs. Slowing down enough to take all the guesswork and surprises out of your experience. Slowing down enough to take your phone call. Forget about those automated computer systems that you’re used to having answer your call for help, because here at Southern Advantage, we take each and every phone call personally, the way it should be.

So what is that we do? Simple.

We deal with modern products of professional video and broadcast equipment, but it doesn’t stop there. What makes us truly unique is that we also specialize in stocking and repairing discontinued formats like S-VHS/VHS, 8mm, Hi8, Digital 8, Betamax and much more!', E'[''electronics'', ''professional electronics'', "vcr''s", ''camcorders'', ''video mixers'', ''professional recorders / players'', ''government contracting'', ''educational institution contracting'', ''vcr repair'', ''overseas electronics'', ''repair'', ''units'', ''sell'', ''s-vhs/vhs'']', E'https://www.southernadvantage.com', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Huntersville, North Carolina, United States', E'Huntersville', E'North Carolina', E'United States', E'[''1-800-632-6076'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/southernadvantage', E'https://www.twitter.com/soadv_', NULL, E'https://www.instagram.com/southernadvantage', E'9466254'),
