  (E'Debbie', E'Russell', E'Dispatcher', E'Apollo Plumbing and Drain Cleaning', NULL, E'debbie@apolloplumbing.net', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Greater Seattle Area United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Operations', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/debbie-russell-04248ab9', NULL, E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/apollo-plumbing-llc', E'Consumer Services', E'Back in 2005, Dan Barger decided there had to be a better way to provide plumbing here where he grew up. He had worked with big corporate plumbing companies and felt there was something missing—a personal touch.

So, he started Apollo Plumbing. It’s not just a family-owned business, it’s a place where customers'' concerns get personal attention from our trained, professional plumbers. In fact, that’s our goal: we strive to be your personal plumber.

That’s why we’re always ready right now: You call. We come. It’s fixed. Guaranteed. That’s plumbing with a personal touch.

