  (E'Renée', E'Martine', E'Outside Sales Specialist', E'Hard Rock Custom Countertops', NULL, E'renee@hardrockgraniteandtile.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Melissa, Texas, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Sales', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/renée-martine-97680b17', E'I’ve built a solid career in the tile and stone industry, covering residential and commercial B2B/B2C sales and design applications from 2006 to the present. When the market shifted in 2009, I broadened my expertise into executive administration, management, event logistics, web design, and digital marketing strategies. I’m a fast learner and self-starter with strong time-management skills, ready to contribute and grow within a results-driven organization.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hard-rock-granite-and-tile-inc-', E'Construction', E'Transforming Spaces, One Custom Countertop at a Time! 

