 and employment experience. I believe my interpersonal and problem-solving abilities will provide an invaluable asset to any team.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/south-bay-hardware-inc', E'Wholesale', E'Hardware Procurement | Division 08 & 28 Coordination | Multi-Family & Commercial Smart Lock Solutions

