  (E'Charles', E'Godron', E'Customer Support', E'HQI Hydraulics', NULL, E'charles@hqihydraulics.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Des Moines, Iowa, United States', E'United States', E'Manager', E'Operations', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/charles-godron-09797412a', NULL, E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hqi-hydraulics', E'Repair and Maintenance', E'Here at HQI Hydraulics, we pride ourselves on being a premier hydraulic sales and service company. Started in 1979, we have 30+ years of work experience to help solve any problem that you might need a solution for. With a vast amount of experience, our service technicians are able to repair items with speed and efficiency while maintaining a high standard of quality. HQI Hydraulics is dedicated to ensuring that clients receive outstanding customer service and high quality repair work, by making them our top priorities. Our services include; cylinder machining and repair, sealing components and kits, hydraulic hose and steel fluid line fabrication, hydraulic pump and motor repair. Construction, municipal, and industrial manufacturing companies are just a few of the industries that HQI Hydraulics provides services to. HQI Hydraulics also offers replacement equipment that may be needed; from hydraulic rams and cylinders to floor jacks and hydraulic hoses, as well as concrete breakers for construction machinery, such as skid loaders and excavators. Hydraulic equipment is important in many settings, from construction sites to auto repair shops. If your hydraulic equipment is having problems, our experienced, hands on team can handle the repairs. We are located at 3400 Delaware Ave, Des Moines, Iowa, 50313. 

