  (E'Dillon', E'Conway', E'glazier', E'Naugatuck Window & Glass', NULL, E'dillon.conway@naugatuckwindowandglass.com', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Seymour, Connecticut, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Trades', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/dillon-conway-a64669200', NULL, E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/naugatuck-window-%26-glass', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'Your windows and doors are importance pieces to your home or business. Having them properly fitted, installed, and replaced is crucial to maintaining the overall image and comfort of your residential or commercial property. Naugatuck Window & Glass provides Naugatuck, CT and the surrounding areas with custom windows and doors suited to your specific needs. Whether you would like storm windows and doors installed on your home to ensure your safety, or a new storefront window to polish off your business, our team can do it all. We work with the best brands and equipment to give you seamless service from start to finish.

