  (E'Sarah', E'Horton', E'Marketing & Customer Service Associate', E'Shield Roof Solutions', NULL, E'sarah@shieldup.co', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Greenville, South Carolina, United States', E'United States', E'Specialist', E'Marketing', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/skhorton13', E'Highly motivated marketing professional with proven experience in digital advertising, social media management, email marketing, and content creation. Skilled in SEO optimization, website design and content development, and brand identity projects including logos and promotional materials. Proficient in managing campaigns across Google Ads, Meta Business Suite, and Yelp, while analyzing performance data to refine strategies and maximize results. Backed by an extensive background in client relations, recognized for exceptional communication, relationship building, problem solving, and attention to detail. By combining a customer-first mindset with creative and data-driven strategies, I deliver marketing solutions that engage audiences and strengthen brand loyalty.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/shieldroofsolutions', E'Wholesale Building Materials', E'Shield Roof Solutions supplies premium PodRoof kits–modular, ready-to-assemble metal roof systems designed to attach to shipping containers or other support structures without welding. Crafted from high-grade American steel and backed by a 20-year guarantee, our products offer long-lasting protection for garages, workshops, shelters, and more.

We make it easy for customers to build with confidence. Every kit includes all necessary hardware, engineered diagrams, and optional add-ons like awnings, carports, and tarp end walls. Whether you''re shielding equipment, creating a workspace, or building a greenhouse, our systems combine strength, style, and simplicity.

Our Product Line Includes:
- PodRoof Kits: Core modular roof systems for containers and structures.
- PodRoof Awnings & Covers: Extensions and overhangs for added sun, rain, and wind protection.
- Tarp End Walls: Flexible enclosures for full weather shielding.
- Carports & Standalone Awnings: Sheltered parking and shade structures.
- Greenhouses: Steel-framed environments for growing and gardening.

We also offer custom sizing, configurations, and finishes, with 14 paint color options for roof panels, trim, and gutters–so you never have to sacrifice form for function.

Our systems are designed for ease of assembly, anchoring securely via container pinpoints with no field welding required. From quote requests and engineering support to installation guidance, we’re here to help every step of the way.', E'[''construction'', ''shipping'', ''storage'', ''roofing materials'', ''construction roofing'', ''roofing panels'', ''portable roofing systems'', ''shipping container'', ''shipping container roofing systems'']', E'https://www.shieldup.co', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'Greenville, South Carolina, United States', E'Greenville', E'South Carolina', E'United States', NULL, NULL, E'[''humanity'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
