  (E'Jordan', E'Medina', E'Sales Manager', E'GENESIS GLASS INSTALLATIONS, INC.', NULL, E'jordan@genesisglass.net', E'good', E'ok', E'99%', E'A-Leads', NULL, NULL, E'Highland, California, United States', E'United States', E'Manager', E'Sales', E'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jordan14medina', E'A Skilled Nursing Assistant is observant, compassionate, patient, engaged, motivated, sharp, and above all caring. So many lives on a daily basis depend on the care and treatment that nurses provide, which is why I chose to pursue this career. Throughout the years I have honed these skills to be the best caregiver I can be, however, there is one skill that I lack, selling myself. So instead I will provide a list of some things about me and my work. 1) I have always been told that I am a personable person. A vital skill that all Nursing Assistants need is the ability to engage with their patients. Every job I have had in the past has helped me develop this skill to its fullest extent. Working as a sales representative for a construction company has especially helped with this. Even though construction and nursing are on opposite sides of the job spectrum, both jobs require understanding and engagement with people. 2) Before my first Nursing Assistant position I was already caring for a large group of people, and by that I mean the eight siblings that I am blessed with! Growing up as one of the oldest kids in the family is probably the biggest training excercises I have had in the steps to becoming a nurse. 3) I knew that nursing was what I wanted to do since I was a kid and I have stuck with it. My weekends and summers in high school were spent volunteering at local nursing facilitees. 4) What sets me apart from others is the fact that I would do this job for free. Nursing isn''t just a paycheck for me, it is a passion.', E'https://www.linkedin.com/company/genesis-glass-installations-inc.', NULL, NULL, E'[''construction/building materials'', ''glass installation'', ''glass backsplashes'', ''storefronts'', ''commercial glass'', ''customer service'']', E'https://www.genesisglass.net', E'2-10 employees', NULL, E'SAN BERNARDINO, California, United States', E'San Bernardino', E'California', E'United States', E'[''909-386-0520'']', E'[''contact@genesisglass.net'']', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'https://www.facebook.com/gginstallation', E'https://www.twitter.com/gginstallation', NULL, NULL, NULL),
