We install residential, commercial and industrial roofs.

Our Roof Technicians are experienced “Journeymen” Roofers, not just some new comers to the roofing industry.

Whether you need a complete re-roof or just repair work and maintenance to prolong the life of your roof, Blue Shoe can help!

We are approved/authorized installers for most major roofing manufacturers.

We at Blue Shoe guarantee that you will receive personalized service for any and all of your roofing needs.

Members of the Roofing Contractors Association.

